Libgdx is a cross-platform Java game development framework based on 
OpenGL (ES) that works on Windows, Linux, Mac OS X, Android, your
WebGL enabled browser and iOS.
http://libgdx.badlogicgames.com/

Currently working on desktop and Android.

You may need to run gdx-setup-ui.jar to configure projects.

Music from https://musopen.org

Character sprites taken from PatchCon: Defend the Library
Portaits and projectile sprites taken from Scarlet Weather Rhapsody and Touhou Hisoutensoku.

sprite rips downloaded from http://www.spriters-resource.com/